    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>In a single movement, you quickly attempt to recover from your fall and draw your blade, laced with icy chakra, in a single flash.</em><br />  As a Reaction to being knocked <em><strong>Prone</strong></em> by another creature in range, make a Sleight of Hand check against the triggering creature's AC. Upon success, you immediately end the <em><strong>Prone</strong></em> condition without spending any movement, and make a melee weapon attack dealing your weapon's damage + 1d4 Cold Damage to the target.</p><p>If this jutsu is cast as a <em><strong>Chain 1 or 2</strong></em>, the target creature gains 1 rank of <em><strong>Chilled</strong></em> on hit.<br />  If this jutsu is cast as a <em><strong>Chain 2</strong></em> as a result of being knocked <em><strong>Prone</strong></em>, you gain an additional Bonus Action on your next turn if this jutsu hits the triggering creature.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and increase the Cold damage by 2d4.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
